{
  "stem": "26983.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her husband, of course, was in Birkenau-- sorry, in Auschwitz 1, in the bunker number 11, which was one of the worst bunkers, where they kept people, prisoners from Gestapo in bunker 11. 50 years later I visited it.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But once was a commission, and people think it was Eichmann who came there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he promised Miriam, because he knew her well from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She asked when I will see my husband.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will see him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You will meet him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he kept his word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But only they met on the 20 of-- after the 20 of June, in the crematorium they met.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were some executed, some about 12 or so people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And again, I knew exactly from the man who was there, it's an execution, single execution, done by a decree from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Apropos, from Berlin always came also all these preparations, let's say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The sonderkommando told me, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We will know exactly when, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because we are getting a telephone [? that ?] Berlin-- prepare the ovens and transport of so-in-so, many people, is on the way, or this-and-this will happen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they knew exactly when to start the ovens for new transports.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But when there were single people, like partisans, or in my time, a very famous scientist, they kept even this [? alien ?] or a special way in Germany, and let them work as long as they needed them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then they came singly to Auschwitz, straight to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there they were shot.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
